# Privacy Policy

Effective Date: April 22, 2026

## Overview

Scout is a Gemini protocol browser for iOS. It operates entirely on your device. No data is collected, transmitted to us, or stored on any server.

## Data Collection

We collect nothing. Scout does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal information.

## Network Activity

Scout connects directly from your device to Gemini servers you choose to visit. These connections are made solely to retrieve content at your request. We have no visibility into your
browsing activity.

## Certificate Storage

Scout stores TLS certificate fingerprints locally on your device to support Trust On First Use (TOFU) verification. This data never leaves your device.

## Third Parties

Scout contains no third-party SDKs, analytics, advertising, or crash reporting tools.

## Children's Privacy

Scout does not collect data from anyone.

## Changes

If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted here with a new effective date.

## Contact

Questions: contact@stevedylan.dev
